Program: Omnibus
Title: Marquis De Sade
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jvv
Last Broadcast Date: 02 June 1990
'An explorer of sexuality and of imagination'. A look at the life of the French aristocrat, revolutionary politician, philosopher and writer, famous for his libertine sexuality whose name became synonymous with sadism.With contributions from Ronald Hayman and Margaret Crosland.